## 🔍 Document Structure Overview

```
docs/
├── COMPLETE_PACKAGING_GUIDE.md (THIS IS THE MAIN GUIDE)
│   ├── Quick Start (5 Minutes)
│   ├── Project Overview
│   ├── Complete Workflow (Phases 1-4)
│   ├── Project Details & Requirements (Summary tables)
│   ├── Quality Assurance (Validation checklists)
│   ├── Deployment & Submission (Step-by-step)
│   └── FAQs & Troubleshooting
│
├── PROJECT_REQUIREMENTS.md (DETAILED REQUIREMENTS)
│   ├── Project 1: Course Homepage
│   ├── Project 2.1: Research Paper
│   ├── Project 2.2: HTML/CSS Implementation
│   ├── Project 3: Multi-Page Site
│   ├── Project 4: Responsive Redesign
│   ├── Cross-Project Requirements
│   ├── Accessibility Standards
│   ├── Validation Requirements
│   └── Submission Checklist
│
├── DIRECTORY_STRUCTURE.md (FILE ORGANIZATION)
│   ├── Canonical Directory Structure
│   ├── File Inventory by Project
│   ├── Current vs Canonical Layout
│   ├── File Naming Conventions
│   ├── Migration Guide
│   └── Cleanup & Archiving
│
├── FILE_INVENTORY.md (STATUS TRACKING)
│   ├── Project 1 Inventory
│   ├── Project 2.1 Inventory
│   ├── Project 2.2 Inventory
│   ├── Project 3 Inventory
│   ├── Project 4 Inventory
│   ├── Shared Assets Inventory
│   ├── Deployment Status
│   ├── Validation Status
│   └── Final Submission Checklist
│
├── AUTOMATION_GUIDE.md (DEPLOYMENT & SCRIPTS)
│   ├── Quick Start
│   ├── PowerShell Scripts (deploy.ps1, package_site.ps1, etc.)
│   ├── Python Utilities (upload_22.py, etc.)
│   ├── SFTP Manual Deployment (WinSCP, OwlFiles)
│   ├── Troubleshooting
│   └── Best Practices
│
├── DOCUMENTATION_INDEX.md (THIS FILE)
│   └── Navigation guide and reference table
│
└── README.md (Repository overview - level up)
```

