## 📋 Document Key Features

### COMPLETE_PACKAGING_GUIDE.md

**Use for**:
- Getting the big picture
- Understanding workflows
- Finding answers to common questions
- Pre-submission planning

**Key Sections**:
- Quick Start (5 min overview)
- Complete Workflow (4 phases)
- Project summaries (all 5 projects)
- Quality assurance checklist
- FAQs & troubleshooting

---

### PROJECT_REQUIREMENTS.md

**Use for**:
- Understanding specific project requirements
- Knowing what's graded
- Learning best practices for each project
- Finding rubric criteria

**Key Sections**:
- Detailed rubrics (50-150 points per project)
- Technical requirements
- Examples and templates
- Accessibility standards
- Validation requirements

---

### DIRECTORY_STRUCTURE.md

**Use for**:
- Organizing your files correctly
- Finding where to put things
- Understanding file naming
- Migrating from old structure

**Key Sections**:
- Canonical directory structure (diagram)
- File inventory by project
- Migration guide
- File naming conventions
- Quick reference checklist

---

### FILE_INVENTORY.md

**Use for**:
- Tracking project progress
- Maintaining status for each file
- Pre-submission verification
- Documenting validation results

**Key Sections**:
- Per-project inventories
- Content audits
- Validation status tables
- Deployment checklist
- Final submission checklist

---

### AUTOMATION_GUIDE.md

**Use for**:
- Deploying to server
- Running validation scripts
- Understanding deployment scripts
- Troubleshooting upload issues

**Key Sections**:
- Quick start (one-command deployment)
- PowerShell script documentation
- Python utility documentation
- Manual SFTP instructions
- Troubleshooting guide

