### Key Commands

```bash
# Validate all files
.\scripts\validate_all.ps1

# Create backup ZIP
.\scripts\package_site.ps1

# Deploy to server (requires VPN)
.\scripts\deploy.ps1

# View this documentation
code docs/COMPLETE_PACKAGING_GUIDE.md
```

