## ✅ Verification Checklist

Before starting any project, verify you have:

- [ ] Read the relevant section in `PROJECT_REQUIREMENTS.md`
- [ ] Created correct folder structure per `DIRECTORY_STRUCTURE.md`
- [ ] Created tracking sheet from `FILE_INVENTORY.md`
- [ ] Understand the workflow in `COMPLETE_PACKAGING_GUIDE.md`
- [ ] Know how to deploy using `AUTOMATION_GUIDE.md`

